channel.title: Duke Nukem Forever First Access Club?
channel.description:
so i just bought and installed borderlands.
so i was just about to start it up, but it tells me i need a key for the game, whatever a lot of games require keys on steam. so i open it and im like WTF...
[img]https://img221.imageshack.us/img221/8329/60901470.jpg[/img]
naturally i crossed out the key just in case this was a mistake and this actually is my cd key
